{"title":"绣列宁（图片）","authors":["吴鸣文　许必华"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":5,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"绣列宁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“列宁在流放中”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命导师的这段生活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾有多少诗人写成诗篇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有多少画家画成画。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏州的刺绣姑娘们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也日思夜想，千针万针，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用绒线绣成了自己的画和诗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看，陆巧云多么快乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她仿佛在说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“亲爱的列宁同志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请你再坐一会儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有不多几针就绣好了。”\t  吴鸣文　新华社记者　许必华摄"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}